562
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:58,590
Cảm ơn em.

563
00:32:03,800 --> 00:32:04,350
Cảm ơn em.

564
00:32:35,110 --> 00:32:35,560
Anh…

565
00:32:35,870 --> 00:32:36,430
Ân Quả,

566
00:32:40,390 --> 00:32:41,200
